==Dialogue==
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{A|VO vo ambient w1 greeting molly 103.ogg}} {{A|VO vo ambient w1 greeting molly 104.ogg}} '''Molly:''' Oh, if it isn't (Trailblazer)! Welcome to the workshop!
:{{DIcon}} Let's have a chat...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026941-->
::'''Molly:''' Okay. What do you want to talk about?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_501029601_13-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_501029601_13-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Someone is a happy camper.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026943-->
:::'''Molly:''' Hehe. Well, I did leave that foul Technology Division, and I'm able to do whatever I want now. Of course, I'm happy.
:::'''Molly:''' Naturally, it's all thanks to you, (Trailblazer), Officer Pela, and Serval. Meeting you all was the luckiest break I've had in my life... I am so grateful to you all!
:::'''Molly:''' I just haven't been able to figure out how to repay you... How about this. If you have anything you want repaired, come and find me. I'll do it for free!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How is the workshop treating you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026947-->
:::'''Molly:''' Hmmm. How should I put it? I guess I would say it feels like home, maybe?
:::'''Molly:''' I just did not fit with everyone at the Technology Division. My coworkers wouldn't even acknowledge my existence. There were some people I never spoke to before even by the time I left.
:::'''Molly:''' I had to handle everything by myself. I was never able to share my thoughts and feelings with anyone. But being here at the workshop is totally different. Serval and I have similar interests. We're close friends now!
:::'''Molly:''' Ah, and then there's Pela and Lynx! Those two are great girls. They're like sisters to me now. Haha!
:::{{DIcon|Return}} That's great to hear. Congratulations.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026952-->
::::'''Molly:''' Hehe. Thank you. I've started a whole new chapter of my life thanks to you...
::::'''Molly:''' I'm... so grateful!
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Return}} We've been chatting and chatting, but we haven't talked about your work.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026955-->
::::'''Molly:''' Huh? Ah, you've got a point... Maybe that's because the workshop often doesn't have any business?
::::'''Molly:''' My job is to help Serval with handling some workshop orders. It's mostly repairing mechanism, like heaters and car engines.
::::'''Molly:''' I've loved tinkering with machines since I was a kid, so my work doesn't tire me out. Or maybe subconsciously I don't view this as work...
::::'''Molly:''' ...ah! Maybe that's why I didn't talk about what I actually do at the workshop. So that's it...
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} No worries. I'll leave you to it.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Good luck with your work!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026961-->
::'''Molly:''' Goodbye! Don't be a stranger!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
