:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501026908: Config/Level/Mission/5010269/Act/Act501026908.json-->
::'''Molly:''' Serval told me that the Over and Underworlds are opening up again. I'm thinking of heading back home.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you from the Underworld?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501026977-->
::'''Molly:''' Yes. Have I not told you that? I was born in Boulder Town, and both my parents are native Underworlders.
::'''Molly:''' My dad worked for a long time at the Tempering Workshop in Rivet Town. That's when my interest in mechanics began to develop.
::'''Molly:''' Later, I packed my bags and came here by myself to learn about Belobog's cutting-edge technology. Little did I know, I would be stuck here because of the Supreme Guardian's order...
::'''Molly:''' Now that I've made it professionally, it's time for me to visit home. I can't wait to tell my parents about meeting you all! I'm sure they will be happy to know that!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_501026908-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->)
